  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Anxiety and depression are highly prevalent in people with rheumatoid arthritis (RA).This
      study is to investigate the effect of anxiety and depression on treatment response in people
      with RA using observational longitudinal study design.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
